                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-162" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN WILSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Alders gate-street Buildings. I was with the prosecutor—in turning round my head I saw the prisoner take a hand<lb></lb>kerchief from his-pocket—I told my cousin, and kept my eye on the pri<lb></lb>soner—he walked off the pavement into the street, and dropped the hand<lb></lb>kerchief behind him—I do not know what became of it—some one picked it up—I am quite sure I saw him take it out of my cousin's pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was walking along, and saw a scuffle with a man in the road; I was on the pavement.</p>
